HEADWORD: Senseful
<hw>Sense"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of sense,
meaning, or reason; reasonable; judicious.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Senseful</xex> speech.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Spenser.</au> ⟦ldquo⟧Men,
otherwise <xex>senseful</xex> and ingenious.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Norris.</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Senseless</ent>⟦br⟧
